  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001368.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) After he had blessed Lugal-kiĝeneš-dudu , Enlil , the king of all lands , combined the title of en and the title of king for him : he ruled then as en in Unug , while he ruled as king in Urim ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001368.15",
      "line_range": "15",
      "translation": "(15) In his great happiness Lugal-kiĝeneš-dudu dedicated this ( vessel ) for his well-being to Enlil , his beloved master ."
    }
  ],
